# Local cargo build artifacts: COPYing them in confuses maturin/cargo
# inside the rust-builder stage (host artifacts are macOS arm64; container
# is linux). On Docker layer cache hits, cargo would also reuse stale
# .so/.rlib from a previous source revision and silently emit a wheel
# missing newly-added pyclasses (e.g. BlocksByRoot* after the
# blocks_by_root.rs addition). 2.8GB of bloat in the build context too.
consensoor-p2p-rs/target/
